OL,1,D]S737{kkkc5FHGV driver shortage: Signs 
OL,2,D]S555{jjj25Fpressures are easing, trade
OL,3,D]Suuu{rrzq5Fgroup says                 
OL,4,T#######################################
OL,5, There are early signs the shortage of  
OL,6, lorry drivers will improve, a trade    
OL,7, association has said.                  
OL,9,FLogistics UK, which represents freight 
OL,10,Fand haulage businesses, said the number
OL,11,Fof drivers leaving the profession had  
OL,12,Fbegun to ease.                         
OL,14,FThe group also highlighted more        
OL,15,Ftrainees coming through the testing    
OL,16,Fsystem as a cause for optimism.        
OL,18,FHowever, it said more action was needed
OL,19,Fby the government and industry to make 
OL,20,Fthe sector attractive to new recruits. 
